snippet.title: Legacy Quest Trailer (2018)
snippet.description:
Download the game now for only $1.00!
https://www.noblevalerian.com/legacyquest

Legacy Quest is a retro inspired 2D platformer.  Guide your Little Stonefoot through progressively more difficult levels.  Take your jumping and crouching to a master level as you avoid enemies, spikes, and gaps.  Collect gemstones to destroy the gems blocking your path, but don't lollygag, you're also racing the clock!

32-bit and 64-bit installers available (Windows Only)

Music:
"Skate" by Komiku Licensed Under a CC0 1.0 Universal License at freemusicarchive.org
